name: gv70
description: From exteriors that harmonize strength and athleticism to interiors that maximize the beauty of white space, the unique characteristic of the Genesis GV70 delivers new inspiration to your everyday life.

name: Gv80
description: The second row independent seats and a center console with the cup holders, console box and wireless charging system enhance luxury and convenience, providing a comfortable experience for passengers.

name: G8 ev
description: The Electrified G80, the first EV model by Genesis, presents a new standard for luxury electric sedans with its high levels of performance and technology.

name: G80 SPORT
description: A reborn athletic elegance-the Genesis G80 Sport has inherited the luxurious sensations and conveniences of the all-new G80, blending a perfectly balanced look with a sporty touch only befitting of a luxury sport sedan.

name: G90
description: G90 introduces a bold new direction that premium cars should pursue, with advanced assistance features that make driving easier, along with a variety of new technologies that add value to passengers’ journeys.

name: Gv60 ev
description: GV60 will set a new standard for luxury electric vehicles with a powerful driving performance and various key features based on interactions with customers.The GV60 is the first dedicated EV model with the most dynamic design, representing Genesis’ electrification.

name: Gv70 ev
description: The Electrified GV70 is a luxury electric SUV model that boasts a dynamic appearance, spacious interior emphasizing the ‘Beauty of White Space,’ new driver-oriented technologies, and powerful vehicle performance.

name: Gv70 new
description: Introducing the GV70, a premium urban SUV sporting a design that maximizes the athletic elegance of Genesis, a dynamic driving experience, an interior that further enhances the beauty of white space, and state-of-the-art technology for connected vehicles.
